---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import HostWizard from '../components/HostWizard.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Host a Live Cam, Anywhere — Port of Cams"
  description="Put a live camera on your waterfront — anywhere on the coast, no install trip needed. Ship-and-mount or bring your own camera; we host it and embed a co-branded player on your site. Free listing (one-time $99 camera) or co-branded for $50/mo. Want it fully handled? See Managed."
  activeNav="host"
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="host-hero">
    <div class="host-hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="section-inner" style="position:relative; text-align:center;">
      <div class="host-tag mono">Any waterfront &middot; Any coast</div>
      <h1 class="display host-title">
        Your waterfront, live on your site.<br/>
        <em class="display-italic" style="color: var(--gold)">Anywhere on the coast.</em>
      </h1>
      <p class="host-subtitle">
        We ship a plug-and-play streaming camera; you (or a local handyman) mount it — or bring a camera you already have. We host it, brand it, and embed a live player on your own website. No install crew to fly out, so it works on any coast, not just ours.
        Start free — a one-time $99 for the camera, yours to keep — or go co-branded at $50/mo. Want it fully handled with pro install? <a href="/managed" style="color:var(--gold);">See Managed</a>.
      </p>
      <a href="#apply" class="btn-primary">Apply Now</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Host -->
  <section class="host-why">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Why Partner With Us</div>
      <h2 class="display" style="font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 56px); margin-bottom: 60px;">
        You mount it. <em class="display-italic" style="color: var(--gold)">We do the rest.</em>
      </h2>

      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"></rect><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"></line><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"></line></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Ship-and-mount, no crew</h3>
          <p>We send a plug-and-play streaming camera — included on co-branded, a one-time $99 on the free listing. You mount it (or hand a local handyman 20 minutes) and plug it in. No install crew to schedule or fly out — which is how we cover any coast, not just Hawaiʻi.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Or bring your own camera</h3>
          <p>Already have a camera — a security cam, an old AV rig, a Reolink? We can ingest, brand, and host that feed instead. No new hardware, nothing to wait on.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Your player, your site</h3>
          <p>Go co-branded and a live player — your logo and ours — embeds on your website with one line of code, plus analytics and shareable timelapses. Your view also joins the Port of Cams network, in front of people already watching the coast.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Security -->
  <section class="host-security">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Built From the Ground Up</div>
      <h2 class="display" style="font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 56px); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Security We Spent Months <em class="display-italic" style="color: var(--gold)">Engineering</em>
      </h2>
      <p style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 60px; max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.8;">
        Before we streamed a single frame, we spent months hardening the infrastructure.
        Every decision — from how the camera connects to how viewers receive segments — was designed with security first.
      </p>

      <div class="security-grid">
        <div class="security-card">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path></svg>
          <div>
            <h4>100% Encrypted Feed, End to End</h4>
            <p>Every byte your camera transmits travels over TLS-encrypted RTMP — from the moment it leaves your location to the moment it lands on our servers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="security-card">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path></svg>
          <div>
            <h4>Hardened Private Infrastructure</h4>
            <p>Our streaming servers run on locked-down private endpoints — no public RTMP exposure, no shared ingress. Months of penetration testing and DDoS mitigation are baked in.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="security-card">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 2l-2 2m-7.61 7.61a5.5 5.5 0 1 1-7.778 7.778 5.5 5.5 0 0 1 7.777-7.777zm0 0L15.5 7.5m0 0l3 3L22 7l-3-3m-3.5 3.5L19 4"></path></svg>
          <div>
            <h4>Unique Stream Keys Per Camera</h4>
            <p>Each camera gets a cryptographically unique stream key. Keys are rotated on demand. Even if one were compromised, zero other feeds are affected.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="security-card">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0 1 12 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 0 1-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 0 0 3 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path></svg>
          <div>
            <h4>Authenticated HLS Delivery</h4>
            <p>Viewers receive time-limited, signed segment URLs. Nobody can hotlink or leech your stream. Premium feeds add an additional token layer.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Trust bar -->
      <div class="trust-bar">
        <div><span class="trust-val">TLS 1.3</span><span class="trust-label mono">Encrypted Transport</span></div>
        <div><span class="trust-val">Signed</span><span class="trust-label mono">HLS Segments</span></div>
        <div><span class="trust-val">Private</span><span class="trust-label mono">RTMP Endpoints</span></div>
        <div><span class="trust-val">Zero</span><span class="trust-label mono">Public Exposure</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tiers -->
  <section class="host-tiers">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">What You Get</div>
      <h2 class="display" style="font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 56px); margin-bottom: 60px;">
        Free vs. <em class="display-italic" style="color: var(--gold)">Co-branded</em> Hosting
      </h2>

      <div class="tier-grid">
        <!-- Free -->
        <div class="tier-card">
          <div class="tier-header">
            <span class="tier-label mono">Free Listing</span>
            <div class="tier-price display">$0 <span class="tier-period">/ month</span></div>
            <p class="tier-desc">Get listed and start streaming. One-time $99 for the camera — yours to keep.</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="tier-features">
            <li><span class="check">&#10003;</span> Pro streaming camera — $99 one-time, yours to keep</li>
            <li><span class="check">&#10003;</span> Listed on the public cameras page</li>
            <li><span class="check">&#10003;</span> Unlimited live streaming hours</li>
            <li><span class="check">&#10003;</span> Basic viewer count stats</li>
            <li><span class="check">&#10003;</span> Standard HLS stream delivery</li>
            <li><span class="check">&#10003;</span> No monthly fee</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#apply" class="btn-secondary tier-btn">Apply Free</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Premium -->
        <div class="tier-card featured">
          <div class="tier-badge mono">Co-branded</div>
          <div class="tier-header">
            <span class="tier-label mono" style="color: var(--gold);">Co-branded Host</span>
            <div class="tier-price display">$50 <span class="tier-period">/ month</span></div>
            <p class="tier-desc">A fully-managed, co-branded player on your own website.</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="tier-features">
            <li><span class="check gold">&#10003;</span> Camera included — ships plug-and-play, you mount it</li>
            <li><span class="check gold">&#10003;</span> Co-branded live player embedded on your site</li>
            <li><span class="check gold">&#10003;</span> Your logo + a call-to-action button on the feed</li>
            <li><span class="check gold">&#10003;</span> Hosting + 24/7 support &amp; uptime monitoring</li>
            <li><span class="check gold">&#10003;</span> Daily viewer analytics dashboard</li>
            <li><span class="check gold">&#10003;</span> Automatic timelapses for your socials</li>
            <li><span class="check gold">&#10003;</span> Featured on the Port of Cams network</li>
            <li><span class="check gold">&#10003;</span> Optional sponsor slot — can offset the cost</li>
            <li><span class="check gold">&#10003;</span> Cancel anytime</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#apply" class="btn-primary tier-btn" data-prefill-tier="premium">Go Co-branded — $50/mo</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p style="text-align:center; margin:32px auto 0; max-width:58ch; color:var(--muted); font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:15px;">
        This is the self-serve tier — you mount it, we host it. Running a Hawaiʻi hotel, marina, or resort and want it fully done-for-you — we fly out, install a marine-grade camera, service it in the salt, and cut monthly social clips?
        <a href="/managed" style="color:var(--gold); white-space:nowrap;">Go Managed &rarr;</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sponsorship -->
  <section class="host-sponsorship">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="sponsor-card">
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="16"></line><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"></line></svg>
        <div>
          <h3>Sponsorship Opportunities</h3>
          <p>Premium camera operators can partner with local businesses, tourism boards, and brands for sponsored feeds.
          Your camera's live view becomes a branded experience. We facilitate introductions and handle ad placement logistics.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#apply" class="btn-secondary" style="flex-shrink:0; white-space:nowrap;" data-prefill-tier="sponsorship" data-prefill-adv="yes">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Application Form -->
  <section class="host-apply" id="apply">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Get Started</div>
      <h2 class="display" style="font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 56px); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Apply for a <em class="display-italic" style="color: var(--gold)">Camera</em>
      </h2>
      <p style="color: rgba(245,240,232,0.65); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 48px; max-width: 520px; line-height: 1.7;">
        Four quick steps. We review every application, then ship and walk you through the hardware — you'll hear back within 48 hours.
      </p>

      <HostWizard />
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .host-hero {
    min-height: 70vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding-top: 80px;
  }

  .host-hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 50% 30%, rgba(201,168,76,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #080808 0%, #0a0905 100%);
  }

  .host-tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 8px 20px;
    border-radius: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .host-title {
    font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 80px);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 28px;
  }

  .host-subtitle {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 560px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
  }

  /* Why section */
  .host-why {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--deep);
  }

  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .why-card {
    background: var(--deep);
    padding: 40px 32px;
  }

  .why-icon { margin-bottom: 20px; }

  .why-card h3 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .why-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* Security */
  .host-security {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .security-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .security-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 32px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .security-card svg { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }

  .security-card h4 {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .security-card p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .trust-bar {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 48px;
    padding: 32px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--surface);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .trust-bar > div {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .trust-val {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .trust-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* Tiers */
  .host-tiers {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--deep);
  }

  .tier-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .tier-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 48px 40px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
  }

  .tier-card.featured {
    background: var(--deep);
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    margin: -1px;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .tier-badge {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--black);
    background: var(--gold);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .tier-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .tier-price {
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1;
    margin: 8px 0 4px;
  }

  .tier-period {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  }

  .tier-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .tier-features {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .tier-features li {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .tier-features .check {
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.2);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .tier-features .check.gold { color: var(--gold); }

  .tier-btn {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  /* Sponsorship */
  .host-sponsorship {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .sponsor-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 32px;
    padding: 40px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--surface);
  }

  .sponsor-card h3 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .sponsor-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* Form */
  .host-apply {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--deep);
  }
  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .host-hero { min-height: 60vh; }
    .why-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .security-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .tier-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .sponsor-card { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
    .trust-bar { flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 24px; }
    .form-wrapper { padding: 32px 24px; }
  }

</style>

